1. Update tailwind.config.js dengan custom colors dari color.css
2. Buat CSS variables untuk light/dark mode
3. Implementasi theme switcher component
4. Test color consistency across components

Pseudocode:
```
// tailwind.config.js
theme: {
  extend: {
    colors: {
      primary: 'var(--color-primary)',
      secondary: 'var(--color-secondary)',
      // ... other brand colors
    }
  }
}

// CSS variables setup
:root {
  --color-primary: /* light mode values */
}

[data-theme="dark"] {
  --color-primary: /* dark mode values */
}
```

1. Buat BaseCrudComponent abstract class
2. Implementasi traits untuk common functionality
3. Base table component dengan sorting
4. Modal components untuk create/edit
5. Bulk actions functionality

Pseudocode:
```
abstract class BaseCrudComponent extends Component
{
    public $search = '';
    public $sortField = 'id';
    public $sortDirection = 'asc';
    public $perPage = 10;

    abstract protected function getModel();
    abstract protected function getColumns();

    public function render()
    {
        return view('livewire.base-crud', [
            'items' => $this->getFilteredData()
        ]);
    }
}
```

1. Buat BootcampCrudComponent extends BaseCrudComponent
2. Form validation dan rules
3. Relasi dengan Batch dan Enrollment
4. Image upload untuk bootcamp
5. Status management

Pseudocode:
```
class BootcampCrudComponent extends BaseCrudComponent
{
    protected function getModel() { return Bootcamp::class; }

    public function store()
    {
        $this->validate([
            'title' => 'required|string|max:255',
            'mode' => 'required|in:online,offline,hybrid',
            // ... other rules
        ]);

        Bootcamp::create($this->getFormData());
    }
}
```

1. UserCrudComponent dengan role management
2. Role dan Permission CRUD
3. User role assignment
4. Bulk user operations
5. User profile management

Pseudocode:
```
class UserCrudComponent extends BaseCrudComponent
{
    public function assignRole($userId, $roleId)
    {
        $user = User::find($userId);
        $user->roles()->sync([$roleId]);
        $this->emit('roleAssigned');
    }

    public function bulkAction($action, $userIds)
    {
        switch($action) {
            case 'activate':
                User::whereIn('id', $userIds)->update(['is_active' => true]);
                break;
        }
    }
}
```

1. OrderCrudComponent dengan payment tracking
2. PaymentCrudComponent dengan status management
3. VoucherCrudComponent dengan usage tracking
4. BlogPostCrudComponent dengan rich text editor
5. Advanced filtering dan export functionality

Pseudocode:
```
class OrderCrudComponent extends BaseCrudComponent
{
    public function updatePaymentStatus($orderId, $status)
    {
        $order = Order::find($orderId);
        $order->payment_status = $status;
        $order->save();

        // Send notification
        $this->emit('paymentStatusUpdated');
    }

    public function exportOrders($filters)
    {
        return Excel::download(new OrdersExport($filters), 'orders.xlsx');
    }
}
```

